---
// Hero section. Edit copy here. Anchors CTA to #projects on the same page.
---

<section class="pt-16 pb-12 sm:pt-20 sm:pb-16">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <img
      src="/razvan-andrei-surdu-sq-min.png"
      alt="Razvan Andrei Surdu"
      width="160"
      height="160"
      class="w-32 h-32 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 rounded-full ring-2 ring-slate-700 p-1"
    />
    <h1 class="mt-8 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
      I build digital products, from games played by millions to small experiments that scratch an itch
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
      Analytical product lead at InnoGames, builder of small experiments, dad, Ironman finisher.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="#projects"
        class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-yellow-300 text-slate-900 font-medium rounded-lg text-base px-5 py-2.5 transition-colors"
      >
        See what I'm building
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:andrei@surdu.de"
        class="inline-block text-slate-300 hover:text-white border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 rounded-lg text-base px-5 py-2.5 transition-colors"
      >
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
